Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurs across all cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities

Name: Percentage of variants that start with SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion immediately followed by Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurrences that are not followed by SW-Checklist Completed within 7 days
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases where 'SW-Checklist Completed' does not happen

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Manuscript Export Succeeded across the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Number of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion events that occur before any Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in their respective cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that include at least one Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion relative to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Number of variants containing SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion that result in an acceptance (e.g., RW-EIC Accept or SW-EIC Accept)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurrences that are part of cases lasting longer than 60 days
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion directly preceding Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all completed review cycles
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion events that appear more than once in the same case
Metric: the average of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Number of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion instances occurring in cases that eventually reach Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion that are followed by any “due in” or “overdue” activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days, First Look-Your updates are overdue)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that involve Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion relative to all checklist-related activities (e.g., SW-Checklist Completed, SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days, SW-Checklist Completion now due)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Number of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion events that occur in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed appears at least once
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs
